[Your privacy. 
Security.
Samsung believes that there is no privacy without strong security. 
We clearly demonstrate how your information is used and give you full control over what you share.
Don't let others track you
You can choose whether to allow or deny the apps you use to access your data.
See who has accessed
We transparently show all the apps that have access to your data. Check the status of personal data easily and intuitively.
Only you can 'unlock'
Your privacy is highly protected with Samsung's Knox technology, certified by governments and security experts in many countries.
Samsung's promise for continuous security support
We keep our security system up-to-date by constantly updating it to protect against evolving security threats and vulnerabilities.
Learn more details about the privacy protection feature and security]